author: imario
msg: setFTPFileEntryParserFactoryKey: allows to set the "key" used in FTPFileEntryParserFactory. In case of the default commons-net implementation this can be a FQCN (which could be your own implementation) or one of the already known ftp-entry parsers - see org.apache.commons.net.ftp.parser.DefaultFTPFileEntryParserFactory for details.
